storyInfo: After helping Tecno, Iana and Doc visit the street art community, but get into a misunderstanding with the respected firefighter Diaz, and take their first tour of the community's culture while on the run.

attributes.content: Anything else I can help with?
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: No, my friend is coming. She'll take care of the rest.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: I came as soon as I heard. What happened? Let me take a look.
attributes.name: Community Resident

attributes.content: Hey, don't grab my head. And don't lift my skirt with so many people watching.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Well, you look alive enough.
attributes.name: Community Resident

attributes.content: Thanks to these two. They helped me when I had a flare-up.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Just doing what any doctor should.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: There aren't many doctors like you left. Most can't run away fast enough when they find out about our condition.
attributes.name: Community Resident

attributes.content: If you're here to take care of her, then we'll be leaving.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Wait! Here's my card. Please feel free to visit my massage parlor any time. 20% off for you amigos!
attributes.name: Community Resident

attributes.content: Thank you, but I don't think we'll needâ€”
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: She's good, you know. Whenever we get an ache or pain, all of us go right to her.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: I'm a physician, I know how to take care of myself. I don't need any help.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Just try it, sir.
attributes.name: Community Resident

attributes.content: Please, keep your distance, ma'am.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: The woman takes a few steps back, puts on a pair of gloves, then snaps her fingers.
Sure. I can do it from this distance.
attributes.name: Community Resident

attributes.content: You can touch me from there?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Ahem... I've heard of people claiming the ability to perform therapy from afar. Whether it's called 'Qi' or some other name, most research indicates that it's pseudoscieâ€”
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: As the woman's fingers move through the air, the pair feel a warm sensation on their shoulders, and soon feel a sense of comfort that envelopes them gently.
Oh... my stress and anxiety... all gone...
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Am I imagining it? I feel so good... oh...
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Well... I guess I can forget the research...
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: What? Someone stole the meds?
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: This is no joke, Ernesto. We have a lot of Infected in the community who need those meds.
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: We apologize for failing to deliver. We'll try to make up for it.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: You don't really think money will do it, do you?
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: If we can't find the meds, I'll try to obtain an equivalent amount of medicine in a timely manner.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Sorry, SeÃ±or Ernesto. I'm just nervous.
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: Did you see the robbers? We have plenty of eyes and ears here. Maybe we can help.
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: That's what felt strange. It looked like a prepared ambush. Rhodes Island has always treaded carefully around here, trying not to make enemies...
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: I can't imagine why anyone would target us.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Maybe they had their eyes on your meds. Suppressants fetch a good price on the black market.
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: They were very professional. Quick and efficient.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Are our meds really worth that kind of effort? And also, I think I heard the sound of gunfire while we were running.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Guns... pros, again. I'm glad Reynell thinks so highly of us.
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: You think someone is targeting your community?
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Our grudge with Reynell goes back a long way. But I never thought he would do something so dirty...
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: What's with the commotion downstairs?
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Sounds like someone's condition flared up while they were outside and got help from kind passersby. People are gathering to thank them.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: We always repay acts of kindness. Let me see their faces...
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: Say, haven't I seen them before?
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: The man picks up yesterday's newspaper and flips to the gossip section, pausing at its title: 'No one can stand him! Reynell changes bodyguards AGAIN.'
Subtitle: 'Exclusive report: Four guards, two shifts? Who are they?'
Hey... they look really like the ones down there.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Looks like we really have to 'repay' their 'kindness.'
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: I feel like I've been born again... It's hard to describe.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Thank you... It's such an astonishing massage technique.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: I learned it in Kjerag. I had to climb Mt. Karlan in a snowstorm to convince the Saintess there to teach me.
attributes.name: Community Resident

attributes.content: Pah, you came here from Siracusa what, seven or eight years ago? When did you have the time to go to the Snow Realm? Don't believe her tall tales.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Hey, I resent the accusation!
attributes.name: Community Resident

attributes.content: Well, thank you for the massage. But we should goâ€”
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Reynell has a lot of people working for him. A couple less won't make any difference.
How about you stay a little while longer and enjoy our hospitality?
Er...
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: PapÃ¡? What's the matter?
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Why are you with these medicine robbers? Why did you bring them here?
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: ...Medicine?
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Yes, medicine for Oripathy! They stole it!
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: Stole? It couldn't be them! They don't even know what Oripathy is!
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: We don't know anything about any medicine. Could there be a misunderstanding?
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Misunderstanding? Who else but Blacksteel and you dress like mercenaries and use guns in these parts?
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: We were just bringing the girl back.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Well, if there's a misunderstanding, we'll clear it up. Take them in!
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: The duo see Diaz's aide raise his staff.
While they cannot imagine how the light at the tip of the staff would do damage, they instinctively sense the approaching danger.
Run, Kateb!
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Look out!
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Come on, you gun-toting thugs! I dare you to set foot in this neighborhood!
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: You were too fast, I couldn't catch you. Where are they?
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Hiding.
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: What are you doing standing there? Find them!
attributes.name: Diaz

attributes.content: Move, move!
attributes.name: Diaz's Aide

attributes.content: What was that? Magic?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: I think they called it Originium Arts. But I guess magic is fine.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: We need to find a way out. The exits are all guarded.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Cover me. I'll control the replicate.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Ready.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Gemini Replicator active.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Hey, where did they go?
attributes.name: Confused Community Resident

attributes.content: Not here, not there...
attributes.name: Lazy Community Resident

attributes.content: Where did she come from?!
attributes.name: Confused Community Resident

attributes.content: Right in the middle of the road!
attributes.name: Confused Community Resident

attributes.content: Bows, crossbows, launchers, Arts Units... all sorts of weapons point towards the gemini decoy in the middle of the road.
Even Iana is speechless at the reception.
Well... talk about a warm welcome.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Bows, crossbows, bombs, 'magic'... hmph.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Let's go while they're distracted by the decoy. It won't take long for them to figure it out.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Maybe we should get in touch with Ela, see what's going on. I'm just so confused right now...
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: No, I'm sure it's not Reynell's guys. His guards have been busy getting whipped by Shuhrat.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Are you sure he's telling the truth?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: I'm sure. He hasn't had a chance to give an order like that today.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: But the people here seem sure that we stole their medicine.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: That's not important. What's important is that we get out of that neighborhood ASAP...
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: It's dangerous for you two to continue, given their special powers. Do you need support?
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: No. Their Originium Arts are impressive, but they're just a disorganized mob. I know how to protect myself, and Kateb's here with me.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: ...Get in touch if anything happens.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: I will.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: They've dispersed, Meijer. Time to move.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Okay, let's go.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Alright, I've taken a look from up high. The district is roughly divided into three areas: the outer ring, the residential district, and that building at the center.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Which is always patrolled by guys with magic wands. There must be someone or something important there.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: That's not important. We're steering well clear of it anyway.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: What about going through the residential area? I didn't see anyone armed. It seems to be a safe path.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Or it could be more dangerous.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: True... common sense doesn't apply to this planet.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Wahâ€”Wahâ€”
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Right

attributes.content: Don't cry, babe, daddy will sing you a song.
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Right

attributes.content: Where are you flying, tired fowlbeastâ™ª
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Right

attributes.content: Towards tomorrow's windâ™ª
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Right

attributes.content: Don't you knowâ™ª
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Right

attributes.content: Your wings are for todayâ™ª
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Right

attributes.content: (Whisper) Asleep, finally...
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Right
Doc
attributes.content: I didn't think I would hear a song like that here.

attributes.name: Doc
attributes.content: Yikes!
attributes.joined: I didn't think I would hear a song like that here.Yikes!

attributes.content: What happened?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Something just dashed past my feet. Rat, snail... I'm not sure. It's too dark.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: This is their garbage dump. No wonder no one comes here.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: The way out is just ahead. You should be glad that people don't come to this stink heap.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Hostiles?!
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: No, just light from that window.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Why would they do this in their own home?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Oh, thank you so much, honey. That fowlbeast just kept running.
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Left

attributes.content: Well, it's not running anymore. Now we canâ€”
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Left

attributes.content: Oh no, it's waking up again! Arts like that just don't work here!
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Left

attributes.content: (Loud fowlbeast crowing)
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Left

attributes.content: Oh no, she's waking up again!
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Right

attributes.content: (Loud baby crying)
attributes.name: Sound from Window on the Right

attributes.content: Ha...
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: I guess Originium Arts isn't the answer to everything.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Look at the colored acrylic boards on the walls. Only people who think of this place as home would put up decorations with no practical use like those.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Same goes for the graffiti on this side. The scenes, figures and decorations don't look like casual doodles.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Every picture seems to tell a story.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Wh-What are you doing here?
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Er, girl, we...
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Calm down. We didn't do what that gentleman accused us of... It's a misunderstanding.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: I... I don't know. You helped me, but...
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: We mean no harm... You know that, girl.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Go right once you leave the alley. The left side may look empty, but sometimes PapÃ¡ goes out there to smoke.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: I was just taking out the trash. I didn't see anything.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: You...
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: (Whisper) We should go, Kateb.
attributes.name: Iana
